{
  "id": "6146f4d4f10c47001d1b5e4a",
  "title": "人名の表記",
  "created": 1632040151,
  "updated": 1632041712,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "6146f4d4f10c47001d1b5e4a",
      "text": "人名の表記",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1632040151,
      "updated": 1632040151
    },
    {
      "id": "6146f4d65b98c20000340dd0",
      "text": "どうしてる？[suto3.icon]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1632040151,
      "updated": 1632040166
    },
    {
      "id": "6146f4df5b98c20000340dd1",
      "text": "[表記揺れ]の話がでたけど、人名の表記法も複数あり、どうすればいいか悩んでいる",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1632040159,
      "updated": 1632040243
    },
    {
      "id": "6146f5355b98c20000340dd3",
      "text": " 本名",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1632040246,
      "updated": 1632040286
    },
    {
      "id": "6146f5555b98c20000340dd4",
      "text": "  これが基本",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1632040278,
      "updated": 1632040292
    },
    {
      "id": "6146f5555b98c20000340dd5",
      "text": " 通名、通称",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1632040278,
      "updated": 1632040297
    },
    {
      "id": "6146f5555b98c20000340dd6",
      "text": "  通名のほうが有名だったり",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1632040278,
      "updated": 1632040304
    },
    {
      "id": "6146f5555b98c20000340dd7",
      "text": "  本名が非公表だったり",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1632040278,
      "updated": 1632040311
    },
    {
      "id": "6146f5555b98c20000340dd8",
      "text": " ペンネーム、筆名",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1632040278,
      "updated": 1632040315
    },
    {
      "id": "6146f5555b98c20000340dd9",
      "text": " 芸名、源氏名、リングネーム",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1632040278,
      "updated": 1632040321
    },
    {
      "id": "6146f5555b98c20000340dda",
      "text": " スクリーンネーム、ログイン名",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1632040278,
      "updated": 1632040325
    },
    {
      "id": "6146f6d979e1130000757d2d",
      "text": "  これでやっている[blu3mo.icon]",
      "userId": "5d89b1f60230ae001779e113",
      "created": 1632040666,
      "updated": 1646747118
    },
    {
      "id": "6146f6ec79e1130000757d2e",
      "text": "  　Scrapboxで言及する場合はTwitterIDで統一している",
      "userId": "5d89b1f60230ae001779e113",
      "created": 1632040684,
      "updated": 1632040724
    },
    {
      "id": "6146f71e79e1130000757d2f",
      "text": "  　それ以外の方法だと表記揺れが生まれやすいので、一つに絞れるTwitterIDを使っている",
      "userId": "5d89b1f60230ae001779e113",
      "created": 1632040735,
      "updated": 1632040767
    },
    {
      "id": "6146f5555b98c20000340ddb",
      "text": "日本語表記",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1632040278,
      "updated": 1632040278
    },
    {
      "id": "6146f5555b98c20000340ddc",
      "text": " 日本人",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1632040278,
      "updated": 1632040332
    },
    {
      "id": "6146f5555b98c20000340ddd",
      "text": "  姓 + 名",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1632040278,
      "updated": 1632040339
    },
    {
      "id": "6146f5555b98c20000340dde",
      "text": "   間にスペースが入ったり",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1632040278,
      "updated": 1632040346
    },
    {
      "id": "6146f5555b98c20000340ddf",
      "text": "   文字の位置を揃えるため、さらにスペースを入れることがある",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1632040278,
      "updated": 1632040351
    },
    {
      "id": "6146f5555b98c20000340de0",
      "text": "  ひらがな表記、カタカナ表記",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1632040278,
      "updated": 1632040388
    },
    {
      "id": "6146f5c55b98c20000340de3",
      "text": "  　漢字表記が基本であるが、あえてひらがな、カタカナを使う人もいる",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1632040389,
      "updated": 1632040453
    },
    {
      "id": "6146f5555b98c20000340de2",
      "text": " 外国人",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1632040278,
      "updated": 1632040514
    },
    {
      "id": "6146f6375b98c20000340de4",
      "text": "  カタカナ表記",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1632040504,
      "updated": 1632040519
    },
    {
      "id": "6146f6375b98c20000340de5",
      "text": "  姓 + 名となるか名 + 姓は現地の習慣による",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1632040504,
      "updated": 1632040538
    },
    {
      "id": "6146f6375b98c20000340de6",
      "text": "  名と姓は中黒「・」で区切る",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1632040504,
      "updated": 1632040542
    },
    {
      "id": "6146f6375b98c20000340de7",
      "text": " 　 例: ドナルド・クヌース",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1632040504,
      "updated": 1632040551
    },
    {
      "id": "6146f6375b98c20000340de8",
      "text": "  ミドルネーム",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1632040504,
      "updated": 1632040556
    },
    {
      "id": "6146f6375b98c20000340de9",
      "text": "   どういうルールなのかよくわからない",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1632040504,
      "updated": 1632041712
    },
    {
      "id": "6146f6375b98c20000340dea",
      "text": "    例: ドナルド・エルビン・クヌース",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1632040504,
      "updated": 1632040567
    },
    {
      "id": "6146f6375b98c20000340deb",
      "text": "    例: ドナルド・E・クヌース",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1632040504,
      "updated": 1632040574
    },
    {
      "id": "6146f6375b98c20000340dec",
      "text": "    例: D・E・クヌース",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1632040504,
      "updated": 1632040580
    },
    {
      "id": "6146f6375b98c20000340ded",
      "text": "  ニックネーム",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1632040504,
      "updated": 1632040586
    },
    {
      "id": "6146f6375b98c20000340dee",
      "text": "   例: ドナルド（Donald）→ドニー（Donney）、ドン（Don）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1632040504,
      "updated": 1632040596
    },
    {
      "id": "6146f6375b98c20000340def",
      "text": "  たまにものすごく長い名前の人がいる",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1632040504,
      "updated": 1632040605
    },
    {
      "id": "6146f6375b98c20000340df0",
      "text": "   例: サド公爵",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1632040504,
      "updated": 1632040618
    },
    {
      "id": "6146f6375b98c20000340df1",
      "text": "    ドナティアン=アルフォンス=フランソワ・ド・サド",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1632040504,
      "updated": 1632040629
    },
    {
      "id": "6146f6375b98c20000340df2",
      "text": "英語表記",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1632040504,
      "updated": 1632040504
    },
    {
      "id": "6146f6375b98c20000340df3",
      "text": " 日本人",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1632040504,
      "updated": 1632040742
    },
    {
      "id": "6146f7215b98c20000340df4",
      "text": "　 名 + 姓 で表記する場合",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1632040737,
      "updated": 1632040951
    },
    {
      "id": "6146f7215b98c20000340df5",
      "text": "  姓 + 名で表記する場合",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1632040737,
      "updated": 1632040960
    },
    {
      "id": "6146f7215b98c20000340df6",
      "text": "  姓（family name）を全て大文字で書く記法もある",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1632040737,
      "updated": 1632040756
    },
    {
      "id": "6146f7215b98c20000340df7",
      "text": "  イングリッシュネームを使うひともいる",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1632040737,
      "updated": 1632040759
    },
    {
      "id": "6146f7215b98c20000340df8",
      "text": "　外国人",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1632040737,
      "updated": 1632040852
    },
    {
      "id": "6146f7935b98c20000340df9",
      "text": "  Donald Ervin Knuth",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1632040852,
      "updated": 1632040852
    },
    {
      "id": "6146f7935b98c20000340dfa",
      "text": "  Donald E. Knuth",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1632040852,
      "updated": 1632040852
    },
    {
      "id": "6146f7935b98c20000340dfb",
      "text": "  D.E. Knuth",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1632040852,
      "updated": 1632040852
    },
    {
      "id": "6146f7935b98c20000340dfc",
      "text": "  Donald Knuth",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1632040852,
      "updated": 1632040852
    },
    {
      "id": "6146f7935b98c20000340dfd",
      "text": " 学術論文などの表記法",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1632040852,
      "updated": 1632040852
    },
    {
      "id": "6146f7935b98c20000340dfe",
      "text": "  Knuth,D.E. ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1632040852,
      "updated": 1632040852
    },
    {
      "id": "6146f7935b98c20000340dff",
      "text": "[* その他]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1632040852,
      "updated": 1632040896
    },
    {
      "id": "6146f7bf5b98c20000340e00",
      "text": "　帰化した場合どうなるのだろう？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1632040896,
      "updated": 1632040896
    },
    {
      "id": "6146f7bf5b98c20000340e01",
      "text": "　結婚して姓が変わる",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1632040896,
      "updated": 1632040896
    },
    {
      "id": "6146f7bf5b98c20000340e02",
      "text": "　香港や台湾だと、イングリッシュネーム（英語名）を持つ人もいる",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1632040896,
      "updated": 1632040896
    }
  ]
}